title: Tangible software solutions Code Converters 17Nov2015 + Patcher
description:
Tangible Software Solutions source converters release 17 November 2015


I've included all the installers for the source code converters,
and my patcher to transform the free editions to standard edition

My patcher requires .NET 3.5, if the Tangible Software Solutions programs work, the patcher should also work fine. :)


I am gonna assume the patcher will continue to work on newer versions of the programs, because of how they check free/pro :)


Step 1. Install the converter(s) you want
Step 2. Run the patcher and select the source code converter executable (don't run it on any other binaries, it'll corrupt them, probably... :D)
(Optional) Step 3. Make new shortcuts, the patcher outputs new binaries without "Free Edition" in the name. :)
Step 4. Enjoy free standard edition versions!


Patcher by the fuzzy red fox! o/ :3
Mono.Cecil and Mono by the Mono team, amazing tool and runtime! o/
